Description:
Start-up of tomcat8 to stop in the middle.
Attachments 
Normal startup of the log file, 20160513startOK.txt
Log file the start to stop in the middle, 20160513startNG.txt

text: You should get a thread dump when the startup stops.

creator: saito@b-s-c.co.jp
text:
thank you very much
I got the dump file

creator: remm@apache.org
text: Ok. There's a deadlock in the application code (caused by locking on object SeiLog), so this is not a Tomcat issue.

creator: saito@b-s-c.co.jp
text: Thank you very match for answering and all your help.
